com.jme3.environment.util

Class CubeMapWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jme3.environment.util.CubeMapWrapper

  • public class CubeMapWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Wraps a Cube map and allows to read from or write pixels into it. It uses the ImageRaster class to tailor the read write operations.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      CubeMapWrapper(TextureCubeMap cubeMap)
      Creates a CubeMapWrapper for the given cube map Note that the cube map must be initialized, and the mipmaps sizes should be set if relevant for them to be readable/writable
